28:55.190 --> 28:57.180
It wasn't a jeep. It was a pickup truck.

28:57.190 --> 28:58.730
Still, it's pretty fantastic.

28:58.740 --> 29:01.140
You all had fantastic plans.

29:02.290 --> 29:03.900
So what happened?

29:04.390 --> 29:05.180
Adrian Monk.

29:05.190 --> 29:06.650
Yeah, Monk. Monk happened.

29:06.660 --> 29:07.930
The guy is relentless.

29:07.940 --> 29:09.850
Pick, pick, pick, pick, pick.

29:09.860 --> 29:11.530
Meanwhile, the case against Douglas Thurman

29:11.540 --> 29:13.130
Took a surprising twist.

29:13.140 --> 29:16.020
Douglas Thurman disappeared.

29:16.080 --> 29:18.550
He had agreed to take a polygraph test that afternoon,

29:18.560 --> 29:19.990
But never showed up.

29:20.000 --> 29:22.280
The next morning, a judge issued a search warrant

29:22.290 --> 29:24.690
For Thurman's apartment and photo studio.

29:26.340 --> 29:27.990
Do you have the warrant?

29:28.430 --> 29:29.590
What?

29:29.600 --> 29:30.760
You gotta be kidding. You just had it.

29:30.770 --> 29:32.140
You had it in your hand.

29:37.130 --> 29:38.110
Where is it?

29:40.790 --> 29:41.910
Here it is.

29:42.580 --> 29:44.260
It was right behind this cd.

29:44.700 --> 29:46.250
I'm in a band.

29:46.260 --> 29:47.910
It's the Randy Disher project.

29:47.920 --> 29:51.460
Do a sort of jazz fusion, punk, rap, kind of folky--

29:51.470 --> 29:53.940
Randy, just give him the damn cd.

29:54.410 --> 29:55.770
You guys like music?

29:56.560 --> 29:59.100
You are gonna love this.

29:59.110 --> 30:01.600
Oh, was that a--

30:01.800 --> 30:03.310
Is that a scratch?

30:03.550 --> 30:04.820
You know what, I should probably

30:04.830 --> 30:06.750
Put it in to make sure it works.

30:15.390 --> 30:17.920
Doug Thurman, s.F.P.D.

30:24.320 --> 30:25.330
Clear!

30:25.740 --> 30:26.810
Clear!

30:28.750 --> 30:29.790
Clear!

30:34.920 --> 30:36.410
Captain.

30:44.260 --> 30:45.800
Is that lipstick?

30:51.510 --> 30:53.260
Sick enough for you?

30:53.730 --> 30:55.030
I guess that clinches it.

30:55.040 --> 30:57.210
This guy's definitely the cosmetic assassin.

30:57.400 --> 30:58.540
The what?

30:58.550 --> 31:00.810
Cosmetic assassin. That's what we're calling him.

31:00.820 --> 31:03.240
Maybe you'd like to hear what we're calling you.

31:03.890 --> 31:05.470
That was probably the low point.

31:05.480 --> 31:07.580
'cause we had that creep in handcuffs the day before.

31:07.590 --> 31:09.050
We never should have let him go.

31:09.520 --> 31:11.070
But the law is the law.

31:11.080 --> 31:12.440
Insufficient evidence.

31:12.450 --> 31:14.300
We put a statewide apb out on him.

31:14.310 --> 31:15.470
But we were too late.

31:15.480 --> 31:17.020
Douglas Thurman's reign of terror

31:17.030 --> 31:18.590
Was not over yet.

31:18.600 --> 31:20.130
Three hours after the raid,

31:20.140 --> 31:22.650
Kate Kindel, a 24-year-old part-time model,

31:22.660 --> 31:24.620
Was found dead in her apartment.

31:24.630 --> 31:26.560
She had been strangled like the others.

31:26.570 --> 31:29.410
And like the others, she had recently posed

31:29.420 --> 31:31.150
For Douglas Thurman.

31:33.820 --> 31:35.120
Even though he was on the run

31:35.130 --> 31:36.590
And the police were closing in,

31:36.600 --> 31:39.160
Thurman could not control his homicidal instincts.

31:40.940 --> 31:42.300
Behind you!

31:51.380 --> 31:54.510
Early that morning, he broke into Kindel's apartment.

31:55.350 --> 31:57.910
Her landlady found her on the living room floor

31:57.930 --> 31:59.430
Three hours later.

32:00.660 --> 32:02.460
Take a bow, Jillian.

32:02.470 --> 32:03.580
Kate Kindel was a girl--

32:03.590 --> 32:05.280
Well done, Jillian.

32:05.290 --> 32:06.510
Well done.

32:10.420 --> 32:11.450
What?

32:12.220 --> 32:13.790
Look, I just said two words to her.

32:13.800 --> 32:15.320
I just said "well done."

32:15.330 --> 32:18.120
You know, I was just congratulating her.

32:18.320 --> 32:19.250
In 12th grade,

32:19.260 --> 32:20.630
She attended a special school for the performing arts.

32:20.640 --> 32:22.500
Like thousands of other young girls,

32:22.550 --> 32:24.820
She moved to california five years earlier

32:24.830 --> 32:26.020
To follow her dream.

32:26.030 --> 32:27.810
She was 27 years old.

32:27.820 --> 32:29.410
She had worked as a cabaret singer

32:29.420 --> 32:31.710
And had appeared in a number of student films.

32:31.890 --> 32:33.500
She had also been found

32:33.510 --> 32:34.920
Brutally strangled.

32:42.670 --> 32:44.620
Took her lipstick, of course.

32:46.750 --> 32:48.210
It's a little dark.

32:48.220 --> 32:49.800
I could use some light.

32:51.410 --> 32:52.840
Thank you.

32:56.960 --> 32:58.250
This is Stottlemeyer.

32:58.260 --> 33:00.460
It was the news they had all been waiting for.

33:00.470 --> 33:03.050
Douglas Thurman had been spotted in san racine

33:03.060 --> 33:04.800
300 miles away

33:04.880 --> 33:06.650
In a cheap motel.

33:08.800 --> 33:10.700
One hour later, as a s.W.A.T. Team moved in,

33:10.710 --> 33:14.240
Douglas Thurman chose to end the drama himself.

33:17.600 --> 33:19.550
With a single bullet to the head,

33:19.560 --> 33:22.730
Thurman had claimed his final victim.

33:24.440 --> 33:26.920
He has solved his 100th case.

33:26.930 --> 33:28.820
Thanks to him, the people of san francisco

33:28.830 --> 33:31.970
Will wake up tomorrow in a safer, brighter city.

33:32.220 --> 33:35.170
But for Adrian Monk, perhaps the most successful

33:35.180 --> 33:37.870
Homicide detective in the world today,

33:38.150 --> 33:41.100
The night is never-ending.

33:51.790 --> 33:54.490
To mr. Monk, the man of the hour.

33:54.500 --> 33:56.030
Don't be surprised if hollywood producers

33:56.040 --> 33:58.470
Come knocking down your door because you're good, my friend.

33:58.480 --> 33:59.100
You're a star.

33:59.110 --> 34:01.310
Cheers. Hear, hear.

34:01.320 --> 34:03.000
San racine is south.

34:04.020 --> 34:05.130
Excuse me?

34:05.140 --> 34:07.140
Thurman had mexican currency in his wallet

34:07.150 --> 34:08.370
When he killed himself.

34:08.380 --> 34:11.100
He was heading for mexico.

34:11.120 --> 34:12.230
So what?

34:12.239 --> 34:14.340
So Kate Kindel, the fourth victim,

34:14.350 --> 34:16.159
Lived 50 miles north.

34:16.780 --> 34:19.380
Why would he go out of his way like that?

34:19.389 --> 34:21.350
And wasn't she strangled from behind?

34:21.360 --> 34:22.710
All the other victims

34:22.719 --> 34:24.340
Were strangled from the front.

34:24.350 --> 34:26.050
Yeah, you're right, she was strangled from behind.

34:26.060 --> 34:27.110
Right.

34:27.739 --> 34:31.190
Douglas Thurman did kill victims one, two, and three.

34:31.199 --> 34:33.150
We were right about that.

34:33.550 --> 34:37.090
But somebody else killed Kate Kindel.

34:37.100 --> 34:39.780
Well, the case is over, mr. Monk.

34:39.790 --> 34:41.250
I don't think so.

34:41.409 --> 34:43.310
Yes! Swish!

34:44.239 --> 34:45.989
Ha, nothing but net.

34:47.120 --> 34:48.389
What?

