34:59.890 --> 35:01.320
Well, this is dvr.

35:01.330 --> 35:02.210
That's too bad.

35:02.220 --> 35:04.930
If it was on vhs, we could watch it again.

35:05.130 --> 35:08.340
Dvr is digital. It's better than vhs.

35:09.570 --> 35:11.280
Well, then let's do that.

35:11.290 --> 35:14.530
If we could rewind the tape or whatever it is

35:14.540 --> 35:16.230
Back to the photo studio.

35:16.240 --> 35:17.710
Natalie.

35:18.970 --> 35:20.160
Sorry.

35:20.170 --> 35:21.070
It's okay.

35:21.080 --> 35:22.580
It's only triple overtime.

