37:09.060 --> 37:10.990
I could use some light.

37:11.770 --> 37:13.530
Picture freezer!

37:14.710 --> 37:15.710
Mr. Novak,

37:15.720 --> 37:17.990
I asked you to turn on the light.

37:18.320 --> 37:19.260
That's right.

37:19.270 --> 37:21.340
There are five light switches on that panel.

37:21.350 --> 37:23.020
