37:23.030 --> 37:25.110
It was a lamp right next to me.

37:26.320 --> 37:27.480
How did you know

37:27.800 --> 37:30.070
Which one of those switches to hit?

37:30.390 --> 37:31.780
How did I know what?

37:31.790 --> 37:33.370
You knew that apartment.

37:33.830 --> 37:35.910
You'd been in that room before.

37:36.100 --> 37:38.540
I-i-i'm a little confused.

37:38.550 --> 37:40.170
