37:40.180 --> 37:41.950
Yes, sir, I am.

37:42.680 --> 37:44.530
It all makes sense.

37:44.820 --> 37:47.100
Kate Kindel was your sex mistress.

37:47.110 --> 37:48.680
I knew it.

37:48.720 --> 37:49.840
Sweetheart, he--

37:49.850 --> 37:50.690
What happened?

37:50.700 --> 37:52.480
