37:57.150 --> 37:58.680
Working on this show,

37:58.690 --> 38:00.160
On this serial killer story,

38:00.170 --> 38:01.820
Give you the perfect opportunity.

38:01.900 --> 38:02.630
It's true.

38:02.640 --> 38:04.600
You had access to everything,

38:04.610 --> 38:06.550
All the stuff we kept from the public.

38:06.560 --> 38:08.850
The killer's m.O., the lipstick.

38:08.880 --> 38:10.290
Here's what happened.

38:10.300 --> 38:12.160
You knew the police were planning

38:12.170 --> 38:13.920
To raid Thurman's studio in the morning.

38:13.930 --> 38:15.270
That night,

38:15.280 --> 38:17.220
