38:37.190 --> 38:39.130
You planted the roll of film.

38:41.270 --> 38:43.840
It would look like Kate was just another client.

38:44.260 --> 38:45.850
Just another victim.

38:47.270 --> 38:48.820
It was a perfect plan,

38:48.830 --> 38:50.590
Framing a serial killer.

38:50.600 --> 38:52.830
You should have watched your own show, mr. Novak.

38:52.840 --> 38:54.150
You can't beat the man.

38:54.220 --> 38:56.780
Probably didn't even listen to my cd, did you?

38:56.790 --> 38:58.970
Okay, first of all, you're a terrible singer.

38:58.980 --> 39:01.500
And secondly, you can't go around accusing people.

39:01.510 --> 39:02.830
Where's your proof?

39:06.070 --> 39:07.820
I think I have proof.

39:09.310 --> 39:10.480
What night was it?

39:10.490 --> 39:11.710
July 25th.

39:11.720 --> 39:12.810
