39:28.370 --> 39:29.810
Is this what you need? Yeah.

39:29.820 --> 39:31.910
You can check it for dna, right?

39:31.970 --> 39:33.800
I'll take that, sergeant.

39:43.490 --> 39:44.630
Get down!

39:45.330 --> 39:47.430
Jillian. Somebody call an ambulance.

